root.text:
Hi developers, I would like to inform you that in version 2.9.2 of fuselibs the InterApp.launchUri - InterApp.launchApp API on iOS no longer works (iOS18).

I needed to update the following line in the iOSInterop.uno file:

-- [[UIApplication sharedApplication] openURL:[NSURL URLWithString:uri]];

++ [[UIApplication sharedApplication] openURL:[NSURL URLWithString:uri] options:dict completionHandler:nil];

I hope this helps.

